    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Schematic drawings of Aculops seguieranae n. sp.: AL. Lateral view of anterior body region; AD. Prodorsal shield; CG. Female coxigenital region; em. Empodium; GM. Genital region of male; IG. Internal female genitalia; LO. Lateral view of annuli; L 1. Leg I; PM. Lateral view of posterior opisthosoma. Scale bar: 10 μm for AD, AL, CG, GM, IG, PM; 5 μm for LO, L 1; 2. 5 μm for em." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210377/files/figure.png" ;
